description: How to remove shower plywood…I trace the outline of the new piece on the floor. Then I remove the screws, use my circular saw and complete cuts with an oscillating multi-tool. Now I can fix the old drain and easily replace the plywood 👍🏽🔥#carpentry #plumbing #bathroomremodel
title: How to Remove Shower Plywood - #shorts #homerepairtutor
